12/27/00
  BUG: video break up when there is parity field conflict
  Reason: insert Glue Pic uses the last received picture's DET as the glue
          picture's DTS.  However, at splice point, if there are pictures
          received after the splice point, then glue picture's DTS will be
          wrong.
  Fixed in dpi1129.fls

  Throttle check in: CSCdt06540

  Noted that insertGluePic() does not set topFldFst field.  For black picture
  insertion, we also need to make sure topFldFst and repField are set
  correctly.


